data.description: You Have found it! Ever wanted to be close to EVERYTHING! Then Welcome Home! This cozy, full of natural light including smart lighting, spacious town home is what you have been looking for! Located 10 minutes from HUB Airport, 10 minutes from Camp Creek Market Place , 17 minutes from World of Coco-Cola, Mercedes Benz Stadium, Georgia Aquarium, & not to mention the close proximity to a plethora of stores & restaurants! High ceilings & wooden floors greeting you at walk-in are just some of the amazing features of this home. Ready for your relaxation & privacy as this home's Primary Suite is located on the first level with its two additional bedroom on the second level. Nestled, in a Gated Community with amenities such as a Pool & Playground. Come see your next home or investment property!
